details.entry_closure_time: 30 minutes prior to commencement of Examination
details.banned_items: valuables/costly items, mobile phones, smart/digital watches, other IT gadgets, books, bags etc.
details.allowed_items_inside_venue: e-Admit Card, pen, pencil, identity proof, copies of self-photographs (whichever applicable) and any other items as specified in the Instructions of the e-Admit Card
details.disciplinary_action: Cancellation of candidature of candidate, filing of FIR/police complaint against the candidate, prohibition from appearing in subsequent Session(s)/day(s) of the Examination
